An unconscious and gently snoring Weasel dressed up as a nightclub bouncer.

He is wearing a black suit with a white shirt and black tie.

Even though it is midwinter he is wearing dark sunglasses.

In his ear you can see make out an earpiece with a curly wire which disappears somewhere underneath his jacket.

His face is heavily scarred.

Sticking out of the top pocket of his jacket is a flyer of some sort, you take it.
> x flyer

