The inside of the barbecue contains a tailors shop and haberdashery.

The sign hanging from the ceiling reads 'Elite Cotour'.

It is run by Penelope Spider, and is where you come for all your clothing needs.

Sartorical elegance is one of your few vices, and runs in the family.

Penelope suffers from hyperlight sensitivity, hence the darkness in here.

