> x Penelope

> x Penelope

Penelope Spider, she is black and hairy with piercing red eyes.

She is wearing a miners lamp on her head and is feverishly working away on a weaving machine.

You can see her shooting the shuttle across the warp and weft,  before operating the treadles with her legs to change the position of the threads before shooting the shuttle across again.

Every now and then she takes some of the material and starts whirring away on the sewing machine, using four of her arms to deftly feed and turn the material through it.
> x sewing machine

> x sewing machine
A black and silver Singer sewing machine. It is a clacking and whirring as Penelope feeds material through it.
> x weaving machine

> x weaving machine

A wooden weaving machine, a complex looking piece of machinery.

It makes a clonking noise each time Penelope operates the treadles, and a shooshing noise as she shoots the shuttle across.

