You are in Santa's Workshop.

The workshop is a blur of activity. It is packed with a gang of elves who are working at lightening speed producing presents.

Every so often the Chief Elf shouts words of encouragement, "Come on lads, we can't let the children down!"

Santa is sat in his armchair checking a very long list.

